        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JM for <hi rend="italic">Quarterly Review</hi> [July 1860] in which he is "quizzed splendidly". The Bishop [Wilberforce] misrepresents him often, but clever men think they can write a review with very slight knowledge of the book.</p> 
        </abstract>
